headline: The 5 Best S&P 500 Stocks of the Last 10 Years
summary: Led by Nvidia, the best stocks over the last decade include three other stocks driven by the buildout of AI infrastructure -- AMD, Arista, and Broadcom -- and one defense stock, Axon.
